      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/european-stocks-kick-off-2024-with-gains-as-oil-companies-climb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债券回落，欧洲股市在 2024 年首个交易日下跌，而由于红海紧张局势加剧，原油价格上涨，能源股表现优于大盘。]]></description>
